-- Bain to buy 3Com
-- 
-- Fri Sep 28, 2007 9:40am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/28/us-3com-bain-idUSWNAS511220070928

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - 3Com Corp COMS.O said on Friday it agreed to be bought by affiliates of private equity firm Bain Capital Partners for about $2.2 billion in cash, China's Huawei Technologies HWT.UL would take a minority stake. 

 Under the terms of the deal, 3Com shareholders would get $5.30 in cash per share, representing a 44 percent premium over 3Com's September 27 Nasdaq closing price of $3.68, 3Com said. (Reporting by  Sinead Carew )